verses.text:
Vir - tues are like kind words, Bov-in and the love, Friend-er that sun and rain; Free of sin and guile;
Beau-ti-ful the flow-ers, Shin-ing in the light;
Find time to love the sweet-est, Lov-ing words the best, Yield-ing hope and com-fort; Joy and peace, and rest,
Truth the like flow-ers, Grow-ing by de-grees; Let flow-ers crown your life Up to His 15.
